stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    state "Risk Assessment" as RiskAssessment {
        [*] --> ModelExecution
        ModelExecution --> RiskScoring
    }
    state "Alert Pending Review" as AlertPendingReview
    state "Dismissed Alert" as DismissedAlert
    [*] --> Monitoring
    Monitoring --> RiskAssessment: New surveillance data is received
    RiskAssessment --> Normal: Risk score remains below the threshold
    RiskAssessment --> AlertPendingReview: Risk score exceeds the threshold
    AlertPendingReview --> ConfirmedOutbreak: Public health official confirms the alert
    AlertPendingReview --> DismissedAlert: Public health official dismisses the alert
    Normal --> Monitoring: Monitoring cycle continues
    ConfirmedOutbreak --> [*]: Response workflow starts
    DismissedAlert --> [*]: Alert is closed
